    <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to fulfill your order (e.g., shipping carriers) or as required by law.</p>
    <h3>Cookies</h3>
    <p>Our website uses minimal cookies necessary for site functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:scott@stompguard.com">scott@stompguard.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

